/**
 * STARFORGE TCG - Balanced Starter Decks
 *
 * 10 properly balanced 30-card starter decks, one per faction.
 * Each deck follows strict TCG balance rules:
 *   - Vanilla stat budget: cost*2+1 total stats, with keyword/effect taxes
 *   - Max 0-1 keywords on commons, 1-2 on rares, 2-3 on epics/legendaries
 *   - Card text matches actual keywords in the data
 *   - Proper mana curve peaking at 2-3 cost
 *   - Each faction has a clear mechanical identity
 *
 * Card IDs use the pattern: {race_prefix}_{m|s|st}{number}
 * IDs referenced by LAST_WORDS_UPGRADES are preserved.
 */

